Dependency Injection:

Dependent: if any class is dependent on any other object/value, then we can say it is dependent

Ex: class Employee{
        Address;
        name;
        age
    }


Injection: If any class dependent on any object/value, providing those value from external source, not directly inside class, we are giving the value form outside the class.

Types of injects:
    . Constructor injection
    . setter injection


